Meritage Portfolio Management
Mutual Funds
Where discipline meets common sense





                Mutual funds 
Meritage offers three distinct mutual funds for investors seeking growth potential. Each is focused on a different segment of the market, and each follows the same proprietary investment process we've developed, tested and refined over two decades of successfully managing separate accounts for individuals and institutions. 
The hallmarks of our approach are:

A value-driven mindset, emphasizing a margin of safety between our estimated value of the security and the market price.
Systematic investment process, combining the power of quantitative research with the benefit of qualitative analysis focused on managing risk.
 An opportunistic mentality, leading the portfolio managers to invest in their best ideas, regardless of market cap size, in both domestic and foreign markets.

