Market review






Meritage Portfolios
	Meritage Portfolios are funds of funds that allow you to build a portfolio that managers rebalance according to market movements. The economic backdrop and recent market turbulence have reminded us of the importance to invest in a well-diversified portfolio. In addition to offering great diversification, Meritage Portfolios allow you to stay true to your investor profile, no matter what happens on the marketplace, so that you can stick to your plan to achieve your objectives.
Meritage Portfolios are entirely comprised of third-party funds, which we have selected among the best in the industry. This brings an acute level of objectivity and the benefit of having a portfolio composed of the best blend of discretionary management styles for your profile. 
To obtain more information on Meritage Portfolios, click here or contact your advisor.




